Installation instructions

It's about as easy as I could possible make it! You find Hide & Seek on the
concrete5.org marketplace and install it using the "Extend concrete5" tool 
within your c5 installation.

For manual installation download and place the hideandseek folder inside 
your packages directory, before using the "Extend concrete5" tool.

Hide & Seek will create two blocktypes:
"Hide & Seek": to split content into dropdown divisions
"Hide & Seek Stopper": to manually end dropdown divisions

For any further information please contact the Hide and Seek's 
addon-page at the concrete5 marketplace or the concrete5 community.

Christian Grauer 2012 www.cgrauer.de

